title: Log into Winter League Portal
custom_preconds:
GIVEN User is on winterleagues(qa).mlb.com
AND User test-wlp-user9@mlb.com has permissions to edit/view winter league portal

(Parenthesis can change depending on environment)
custom_steps:
WHEN User types test-wlp-user9@mlb.com into user name
AND types 5*hOUSE*jAPAN: into password
AND selects login
custom_expected: THEN User successfully logins to winter league portal

title: User selects their reserve list
custom_preconds: GIVEN User is logged in as test-wlp-user9@mlb.com
custom_steps: WHEN User clicks on the club name associated with the login
custom_expected: THEN User is brought to that club's reserve list

title: User clicks edit on a reserve list
custom_preconds:
GIVEN User is logged in as test-wlp-user9@mlb.com
AND User is on Club's reserve list

title: User searches for player for reserve list
custom_preconds:
GIVEN User is logged in as test-wlp-user9@mlb.com
AND User is on Club's reserve list
custom_steps:
WHEN User types in First Name and Last Name into box fills
AND Clicks Search
custom_expected: Then players should appear in results box

title: User adds player from search results to any of the three sections
custom_preconds:
GIVEN User is logged in as test-wlp-user9@mlb.com
AND User is on Club's reserve list
AND User has found players in results box
custom_steps:
WHEN User drags a player into Import
AND Selects a checkbox next to a player
AND Selects Add To (Primary/Secondary/Import)
custom_expected: THEN User is added to the corresponding selection of the player

title: User adds an unlisted player
custom_preconds:
GIVEN User is logged in as test-wlp-user9@mlb.com
AND User is on Club's reserve list
AND reserve list is in edit mode
custom_steps:
WHEN User clicks Add Unlisted Player
AND Fills out all required fields on pop up
AND Clicks Add Player
custom_expected: THEN Player is added to section that the player specified in popup

title: User clicks Save
custom_preconds:
GIVEN User is logged in as test-wlp-user9@mlb.com
AND User is on Club's reserve list
AND Players are on the reserve list
custom_expected: THEN All information is saved with blue notification
